                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4831" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0202</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8292 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">集工业软件齐发力，启协同制造开新篇 ——工业软件集成支撑LN船厂实现快速响应协同制造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Set up industrial software to start a new chapter of collaborative manufacturing ——Industrial software integration supports ln shipyard to realize rapid response collaborative manufacturing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">薄洪光，梁利静，唐佳宁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连辽南船厂</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">协同制造、工业软件、生产干扰、生产计划与排产、外包供应商管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">collaborative manufacturing, industrial software, production disruption, production planning and scheduling, outsourcing supplier management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">船舶建造是典型的复杂技术装备项目型生产制造过程。利用有限信息资源，协调复杂的制造及供应链环节使其平顺衔接是一项困难的管理任务，而在多类扰动并存的生产环境下快速、有效协同各环节有序工作更是难上加难。在工业4.0软件化时代，工业软件凭借物联网实现数据采集与传输，承载了更多企业管理功能，已逐渐成为解决协同制造问题的新工具。案例中，LN船厂通过应用APS等工业软件解决了多类生产扰动条件下船舶的建造计划排产问题，使船厂内外部各制造环节节拍同步化；ERP软件重建外包供应商管理模块，实现外包与自制环节的快速响应协同。APS与ERP/PDM/MES等集成应用，有效提高供应链环境中LN船厂协同效率，开启了企业协同造船新篇章。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Shipbuilding is a typical project-based manufacturing process of complex technical equipment. It is a difficult management task to coordinate the complex manufacturing and supply chain links by using limited information resources, and it is even more difficult to effectively coordinate the orderly work of various links in the production environment where multiple disturbances coexist. In the era of industry 4.0, industrial software realizes data acquisition and transmission by virtue of the Internet of things, carrying more enterprise management functions, and has gradually become a new tool to solve the problem of collaborative manufacturing. In the case, LN shipyard solved the problem of ship construction planning and scheduling under the conditions of multiple production disturbances by applying industrial software such as APS, which made the internal and external manufacturing links of the shipyard synchronized; ERP reconstructed the outsourcing supplier management module to realize the rapid response coordination between outsourcing and self-made links. The integrated application of APS and ERP / PDM / MES can effectively improve the collaborative efficiency of LN shipyard in the supply chain environment, and open a new chapter of enterprise collaborative shipbuilding.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业管理》、《生产运作管理》、《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">协同制造；信息技术与工业制造融合；工业软件；抗干扰快速响应协同制造模式；工业制造未来发展趋势</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
